articles.title: Mexican authorities arrest 5 suspects turned over by cartel in deadly kidnapping of Americans last week - Fox News
articles.description: A Mexican official said on Friday that five suspects had been arrested in connection the deadly cartel kidnappings of four Americans.
articles.content:
Five suspects have been arrested in Mexico for the deadly kidnappings of four Americans who had crossed the border from Texas last week, a Mexican official confirmed on Friday.
